com.wm.data

Class MLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.wm.data.MLong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MLong
extends java.lang.Number
    This class is a wrapper for long values and is similar to the existing Java wrapper class Long. However, unlike the Long class, MLong is mutable, allowing you to change the long value that it wraps.
    See Also:
    MBoolean, MByte, MDouble, MFloat, MInteger, MShort, Serialized Form
